Method behavioural requirements:
- The integer array parameter `boxes` must not be null.
- The integer parameter `portsCount` must be greater than or equal to 1.
- The integer parameter `maxBoxes` must be greater than or equal to 1.
- The integer parameter `maxWeight` must be greater than or equal to 1.
- The integer result is the minimum number of trips the ship needs to make to deliver all boxes to their respective ports.